room_title: Escape room "The Passage" by Twisted Limits Escape Rooms in Chicago
room_description: Working on behalf of the mysterious ONEIROS company, your team is tasked with investigating a research site deep underground. There, a group of scientists had recently uncovered an artifact that was pivotal to breaching a metaphysical anomaly known as "The Passage". Believing the researchers had proceeded beyond "The Passage" with the artifact before all communication was lost, you must scour the entire site, retrace their steps, and perhaps even travel beyond "The Passage" as well. ONEIROS needs answers and the missing artifact back in company hands at all costs.
